title: Proposal to pay Dev for November days worked
body:
Proposal to pay Dev for 8 of 30 days of November worked as detailed in forum post (https://gov.rarible.org/t/proposing-the-rarible-dao-accelerator/333) and snapshot (https://snapshot.org/#/rarible.eth/proposal/0x746c0273412457015d0ac74179ba0a316aa8adfcd3b4e35a009bbd81b2840a3f) establishing the Rarible Accelerator.

8/30 * $12,500/month = $3,333,33 in $RARI or stable coin.
author: 0x078eDe7D7174c81D4d3CCA8265f79F464E576013
